cat << EOF
Mlterm is a multilingual terminal emulator on X11. It has full unicode support
and provides several aditional features such as input method support, faux
transparency and picture backgrounds, vertical mode and full
internationalisation support. The input methods supported are xim, uim, scim,
iiimf and kbd.
EOF
